<item>
            <title>[LU-19240] IR: use source NID to filter NID list returning to a client</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19240</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With big NID lists on many networks it makes sense to report first NIDs on the same network as client uses to send RPC, if there is also nodemap filtering is in use then only that network NIDs are returned&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="91508">LU-19240</key>
            <summary>IR: use source NID to filter NID list returning to a client</summary>
